y\ndetermined the mean viscosity. Extrapolating the secondary's radial expansion,\nwe predict that the star will fill is Roche lobe at a separation which is\n1.2-1.3 smaller than the current one. Applying this method to a future sample\nof systems can allow us to learn whether viscosity changes with mass and/or\nnuclear composition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2013 19:59:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
