er claims that the mHz QPOs of M82\nX-1 are the analogs of the Type-C low-frequency QPOs of StMBHs. On the other\nhand, it is possible that the observed relation between the hardness ratio and\nthe QPO frequency represents the saturated portion of the correlation seen in\nType-C QPOs of StMBHs -- in which case M82 X-1's mHz QPOs can still be\nanalogous to Type-C QPOs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2013 20:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-09"}
